      DateRangeBuilder DateRangeBuilder.set​(java.lang.Class<? extends java.util.Date> valueClass)

      DateRangeBuilder DateRangeBuilder.set​(java.util.TimeZone timeZone)
      Configuration method which sets desired time zone which will be used to calculate DateRange.getStart and DateRange.getEnd.
